node.title: House shot at in west Auckland, no one injured
node.description: Police are investigating an incident during which a firearm was discharged at a house in Te AtatÅ« from outside the property in the early hours.
node.content:
["Police are investigating an incident during which a firearm was discharged at a house from outside the property in the early hours.", "", "
File pic. Photo: 123RF
", "Police were called to the scene in Royal View Road in the west Auckland suburb of Te Atatū, just before 12.30am.", "A spokesperson said in a statement that early signs indicated that a gun was fired at a house from beyond the property.", "Several adults were inside the house at the time, however, no one was injured.", "Scene guards remained at the property overnight and a scene examination is being carried out today.", "Police would like to hear from anyone who has information about the incident.", "Information can be passed on via the police number at 105 quoting event number 220425/2681.", "Information can also be provided anonymously to Crime Stoppers on 0800 555 111.", "There will be more police staff working in the area while staff make more inquiries."]
